is, but NESASM also can include other files.</div>ASM6 has INCLUDE and INCBIN. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" />  There is more explanation of the entire ASM6 in README.TXT... it's a really good explanation. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" /><br /><div class="quotetitle">3gengames wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">If you want more help feel free to mail me, I'd be interested in learning a new assembler, too.</div> You are so kind - thank you, but the included README.TXT help is really excellent! And there's a whole strong ASM6 user group here. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" />  And, asking basic questions in this forum can also help others.  Do you agree?</div>

